                    {
                        "unit_id": 1014,
                        "title": "Setting your 3 Year Objectives",
                        "slug": "setting-3-year-objectives",
                        "order": 40,
                        "status": "publish",
                        "content": "",
                        "media": {
                            "youtube_video_id": "qTeAleAXKAs",
                            "banner_image_url": null,
                            "featured_image_url": null,
                            "pdf_template_url": null
                        },
                        "meta": {
                            "course-unit-read": "<h5>Keeping in mind where you want to be when you retire, think about what you want to accomplish in the next 3 years. After 3 years from now, what are the achievable – even if a little challenging – goals that you want to have done. It could be a business that you want to start up, a career move that you want to make, a house that you want to buy, a personal objective that you have or anything like that.</h5>\r\n<h5>Choose 2 objectives from your professional and 2 from your personal side that you want to accomplish within 3 years.</h5>",
                            "course-unit-read-more": "",
                            "course-unit-quotes": "\"Happy people plan actions, they don't plan results.\" Denis Waitley",
                            "course-unit-case-study": "<h5>Thinking of her long term objective of doing well for nature and her community, Vera decides that she would like within 3 years to be working with a non-profit organisation, or a social business that is aligned to her long term goal. To do that, she realizes that she needs to build her experience in this space and identify which would be the organisations that she would like to work with.</h5>",
                            "course-unit-last-related-content": "",
                            "course-unit-customrelated": "",
                            "course-unit-page-show-game": "",
                            "course-unit-page-show-related": "",
                            "course-unit-page-ads": "",
